org.apache.flink.runtime.executiongraph

类 ExecutionVertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.executiongraph.ExecutionVertex
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable

    public class ExecutionVertex
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The ExecutionVertex is a parallel subtask of the execution. It may be executed once, or several times, each of which time it spawns an Execution.

      • getPreferredLocations

        public Iterable<Instance> getPreferredLocations()
        Gets the location preferences of this task, determined by the locations of the predecessors from which it receives input data. If there are more than MAX_DISTINCT_LOCATIONS_TO_CONSIDER different locations of source data, this method returns null to indicate no location preference.
        返回:
        The preferred locations for this vertex execution, or null, if there is no preference.
